{"color": "green", "emoji": "\ud83d\udcac", "event_type": "Agent Message", "message": "The mobile capture is useful, but the desktop viewport still crops the actual tone cards. I\u2019m switching to element screenshots of the stage-detail panel so the review artifact shows the full tone UI instead of the page chrome.", "raw_event": {"item": {"id": "item_143", "text": "The mobile capture is useful, but the desktop viewport still crops the actual tone cards. I\u2019m switching to element screenshots of the stage-detail panel so the review artifact shows the full tone UI instead of the page chrome.", "type": "agent_message"}, "type": "item.completed"}, "task_display_context": {"event_number": 268, "prompt_index": 42, "prompt_name": "41 \u2014 Tone Selection API and UI", "prompt_total": 100}, "timestap": "2026-04-01T19:20:54-07:00"}
{"color": "cyan", "emoji": "\ud83d\udee0", "event_type": "Command Started", "message": "in progress: /bin/zsh -lc \"node --input-type=module - <<'EOF'\nconst base = 'http://localhost:8565/api/v1';\n\nasync function createToneStageSession(title) {\n  const createResponse = await fetch(\"'`${base}/sessions`, {\n    method: '\"'POST',\n    headers: { 'content-type': 'application/json' },\n    body: JSON.stringify({ working_title: title }),\n  });\n  const created = await createResponse.json();\n  const selectGenreResponse = await fetch(\"'`${base}/sessions/${created.id}/selections/genre`, {\n    method: '\"'POST',\n    headers: { 'content-type': 'application/json' },\n    body: JSON.stringify({ genre_slug: 'quest-fantasy', origin: 'workspace' }),\n  });\n  const toneStage = await selectGenreResponse.json();\n  return toneStage.snapshot.id;\n}\n\nconst desktopId = await createToneStageSession('Prompt 41 Tone Desktop QA Panel');\nconst mobileId = await createToneStageSession('Prompt 41 Tone Mobile QA Panel');\nconsole.log(JSON.stringify({ desktopId, mobileId }));\nEOF\"", "raw_event": {"item": {"aggregated_output": "", "command": "/bin/zsh -lc \"node --input-type=module - <<'EOF'\nconst base = 'http://localhost:8565/api/v1';\n\nasync function createToneStageSession(title) {\n  const createResponse = await fetch(\"'`${base}/sessions`, {\n    method: '\"'POST',\n    headers: { 'content-type': 'application/json' },\n    body: JSON.stringify({ working_title: title }),\n  });\n  const created = await createResponse.json();\n  const selectGenreResponse = await fetch(\"'`${base}/sessions/${created.id}/selections/genre`, {\n    method: '\"'POST',\n    headers: { 'content-type': 'application/json' },\n    body: JSON.stringify({ genre_slug: 'quest-fantasy', origin: 'workspace' }),\n  });\n  const toneStage = await selectGenreResponse.json();\n  return toneStage.snapshot.id;\n}\n\nconst desktopId = await createToneStageSession('Prompt 41 Tone Desktop QA Panel');\nconst mobileId = a