{"color": "green", "emoji": "\ud83d\udcac", "event_type": "Agent Message", "message": "Implemented tone selection end to end across backend and workspace. The backend now exposes per-genre tone options and a durable tone-selection endpoint, persists the selected tone into the session snapshot/history, advances the workflow...", "raw_event": {"item": {"id": "item_167", "text": "Implemented tone selection end to end across backend and workspace. The backend now exposes per-genre tone options and a durable tone-selection endpoint, persists the selected tone into the session snapshot/history, advances the workflow to `brief`, and invalidates downstream planning when the tone changes. The frontend now has a real `ToneSelectionStage`, filtered tone queries, concrete tone cards built from catalog hints, and runtime handling for both direct UI selection and accepted chat `select_tone` actions.\n\nVerification completed:\n- `pytest backend/tests` -> `117 passed, 5 skipped`\n- `ruff check backend/app backend/tests` -> passed\n- `npm test` -> `56 passed`\n- `npm run lint` -> passed\n- `npm run build` -> passed\n- `npm run format:check` -> passed\n- Browser QA against the live Docker Compose app confirmed genre-filtered tone cards, absence of cross-genre tones, and transition into the brief stage after selecting `Hushed Wonder`\n\nReviewer summary file: [summary.md](/Users/kevin/code/storyteller/.yolopilot/runs/20260331T205548_storyteller_prompt_pack/41_tone_selection_api_and_ui/summary.md)\n\nScreenshot artifacts:\n- [prompt-41-tone-desktop-before.png](/Users/kevin/code/storyteller/.artifacts/webapp-qa/prompt-41-tone-desktop-before.png)\n- [prompt-41-tone-desktop-after.png](/Users/kevin/code/storyteller/.artifacts/webapp-qa/prompt-41-tone-desktop-after.png)\n- [prompt-41-tone-mobile-before.png](/Users/kevin/code/storyteller/.artifacts/webapp-qa/prompt-41-tone-mobile-before.png)", "type": "agent_message"}, "type": "item.completed"}, "task_display_context": {"event_number": 310,